---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import heroPiano from "../../assets/images/hero-piano.webp";
---

<section
    class="relative min-h-[55vh] py-16 md:py-0 md:h-[65vh] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden"
>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0 bg-[#1A130E]">
        <Image
            src={heroPiano}
            alt="落ち着いた空間でのピアノレッスン"
            width={1200}
            height={800}
            class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-60 md:opacity-50 object-[25%_center]"
            loading="eager"
            fetchpriority="high"
        />
        <div
            class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-[#1A130E]/80 via-[#1A130E]/70 to-[#1A130E]/85"
        >
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="relative z-10 text-center px-6 md:px-4 max-w-5xl">
        <span
            class="block text-xs md:text-sm tracking-[0.15em] md:tracking-[0.2em] leading-relaxed mb-6 text-[#D4C5B9] font-serif font-medium uppercase"
        >
            <span class="inline-block">東京都内</span><span class="inline-block">（江東区・中央区周辺）</span><span class="inline-block">出張・スタジオ対応</span>
        </span>

        <h1 class="font-serif text-white/95 flex flex-col items-center">
            <span
                class="text-lg sm:text-xl md:text-2xl tracking-[0.1em] sm:tracking-[0.15em] text-[#E8E2D9] font-medium mb-3 sm:mb-4"
                >大人のための出張ピアノレッスン</span
            >

            <span
                class="block text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-medium tracking-[0.08em] mb-6 sm:mb-8 leading-tight text-white drop-shadow-lg"
            >
                髙橋遊月ピアノ教室
            </span>
        </h1>
        <p
            class="font-serif text-sm md:text-base leading-[2.4] md:leading-[2.8] tracking-wider md:tracking-widest text-white/90 max-w-2xl mx-auto font-medium"
        >
            ご自宅や近隣スタジオでのマンツーマン出張レッスン。<br />
            初心者からブランクのある再開者まで、<br />
            ご希望のペースや曲に合わせて丁寧に進めます。
        </p>
    </div>
</section>

